channel.description:
Hello everyone, please take a minute before just scrolling all the way down and seeing what this is, ----- Current Developers of URS: 1. Hydromcmac2 - Owner. 2. Billygotshot - Head of CFG Files. 3. aaa801 - Head of Server Management. 4. WildFire - Head of Site Developement. 5. Oblak - Coder. 6. None 7. None 8. None 9. None 10. None ----- I am Dylan incase you didn't know, I am currently starting right now to make a new Runescape Private Server... That, will, be, HUGE. Just like RuneScape only better... You can do commands, build things, I plan to have all Skills, all Capes, all NPC's, training just right... Just like Runescape, only better. I am now in the process of looking for a Crew to help with the designing/developing. I need HEAVY, STRONG, GOOD, Coders... Who know what they're doing. That are familiar with Voids, Ints, Enums, Frames, Timers. If you think you have what it takes to step-up and take a shot at this one-in-a-life-time oppertunity... You step-up now! --- Minimum Requirements: Proper Grammer: (e.g. Not, "hello how r u?" It's, "Hello, how are you?" get the point? Expierience: (e.g. Such as in Private Servers.) Positions needed for filling: If your a CFG Manager (We need 3) please use this form and reply to this thread.
Name: Position: Email: Expierience?:
If your a Java Manager (We need 3) please use this form and reply to this thread.
Name: Position: Email: Expierience:
--- So far, these are all the positions I'd like to be filled, each person may have a Maximum of 2 positions. Proper grammer will look good on your application(s). I am taking this very seriously. ~Dylan Add my MSN For more chatting if you'd like: hydro_mc_mac2@dylancordio.com Check out the forums: ursrsps.smfforfree2.com ---
